article.description: — Quincy Olivari had 20 points as Rice topped Southern Miss 76-68 on Saturday.
article.headline: Olivari scores 20 to carry Rice over Southern Miss 76-68
article.linkText: Olivari scores 20 to carry Rice over Southern Miss 76-68
article.story: HOUSTON -- — Quincy Olivari had 20 points as Rice topped Southern Miss 76-68 on Saturday. Max Fiedler had 16 points, eight rebounds and five assists for Rice (12-8, 6-6 Conference USA). Travis Evee added 11 points. Tyler Stevenson scored a career-high 31 points and had 10 rebounds for the Golden Eagles (7-12, 3-9), who have now lost six straight games. DeAndre Pinckney added seven rebounds. The Owls improve to 2-0 against the Golden Eagles this season. Rice defeated Southern Miss 88-62 on Friday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
